# GroundedExistence — Paper 64: Primordial Ground and Grounded Existence

**Whatever exists is Alpha-grounded. Alpha is primordial, not grounded by other,
not object-level, not temporalized, not null, and not mere infinity.**

Paper 64 unfolds the consequences of the Alpha theorem (Paper 63): to exist
entails Alpha-groundedness; Alpha has the structural properties of primordial
ground. Depends on Alpha (Paper 63).

