- `ContentOf` — entity/content belongs to a ledger
- `GroundedInAlpha` — actuality derives from the necessary pre-categorial ground
- `GroundedByOther`, `ObjectLevel`, `Temporalized`, `Primordial`, `NullGround`, `MereInfinity`

